author: Alex Robert Ross
title: Listen to Frank Ocean's Surprise New Song, "Chanel"
text:
Listen to Frank Ocean's Surprise New Song, "Chanel" He dropped the song on the second episode of his Beats 1 show, 'Blonded.' 
Remember a year ago, when we all sat around and talked about how Frank Ocean hadn't released new music in what seemed like an age? 
Well, a couple weeks on from the release of the Calvin Harris and Migos collaboration, "Slide," Ocean has returned with yet another new song. "Chanel" dropped on the second episode of his Blonded show on Beats 1 on Friday. You can listen to the full track below and read the lyrics to the track, via an aesthetically pleasing Tumblr post from Ocean himself, beneath that. 
Follow Noisey on Twitter .
